>>> Dictionaries (Objects)

Var person = {
name: "john",                                                   // --> name, age, favColour and height are examples of properties
age: 31,
favColour: "green", 
height: 183
};

document.write(person.age);
or:  
document.write(person["age"]);

--> 31


